Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.54,0:00:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.80,0:00:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超级女英雄  天使队  GO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.44,0:00:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放轻松点吧  耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.11,0:00:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,银河天使S
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.49,0:00:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸运  猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挥汗如雨  爱哭的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.06,0:00:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,精力充沛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.56,0:00:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下雨之后没大脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.70,0:00:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种香蕉(怎么可能)凤梨  布丁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.77,0:00:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜欢的事情戒不掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.01,0:00:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽管搞笑被捉弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.51,0:00:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽管宿醉昏沉沉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.08,0:00:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸福的魔咒是展开笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.35,0:00:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Let's go Let's go 天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.06,0:00:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇蹟战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.56,0:01:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快乐的源头是爱  爱  爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.60,0:01:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再来更多的仙境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.27,0:01:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开心痛快棒极了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用赚到了的心情\N兴高采烈的吻一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.97,0:01:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兴高采烈的吻一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.54,0:01:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愿你有个好心情！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.25,0:01:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SHUWA  SHUWA  BUNBUN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.41,0:01:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SHUWA  BUNBUN  耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.54,0:01:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶，那些该死的叛军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.61,0:01:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠我们几个要打这么多\N这样根本打不完嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.91,0:01:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第13区域全灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.51,0:01:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第13区域全灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.15,0:01:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌军已经入侵到第15区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.72,0:01:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这下真的惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.12,0:02:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是一定得撑到援军来才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.56,0:02:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,援军才不会来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.56,0:02:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想也是\N战况这么激烈的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.89,0:02:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不定这会成为\N大家最后的任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.00,0:02:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸…炸虾天妇罗盖饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.90,0:02:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家不可以气馁啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.87,0:02:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是我们的家，不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.71,0:02:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们好好地来保护它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.51,0:02:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吗？好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.08,0:02:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.89,0:02:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.95,0:02:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是我们的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岂能让叛军占领！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是这种斗志！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.00,0:02:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，不可以！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.04,0:02:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家快点趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.04,0:02:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.71,0:03:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#01  浮幽灵含果肉果酱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.36,0:03:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还活着啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.03,0:03:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什么，原来是一场梦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.16,0:03:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.63,0:03:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.64,0:03:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.64,0:03:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,华克中校，我在叫你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.18,0:03:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真讨厌，你是睡昏头了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.09,0:03:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校，你听不见我的声音吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.82,0:03:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校，华克中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，不得了了\N华克中校变得好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是说那个时候佛特你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？是这样的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.44,0:03:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本来就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…佛特…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.68,0:04:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，你听我说啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.65,0:04:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.12,0:04:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，你们看不见我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在跟你们说话啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.92,0:04:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到底是怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.03,0:04:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，真是吓了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.90,0:04:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来只有我一个人\N看得见梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.60,0:04:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺麦德，这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.54,0:04:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都没有发现我的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.44,0:04:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是当然的，因为你似乎已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.64,0:04:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.78,0:04:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请告诉我！我到底怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.91,0:04:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直接了当的说，你已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.79,0:04:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？我什么时候死的？\N为什么会死呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这还用问吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次跟叛军作战的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为了拯救大家\N拿着手榴弹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.80,0:05:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来那不是一场梦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.00,0:05:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时的爆炸真的很惊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.57,0:05:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在那个时候\N也受到很严重的损伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.58,0:05:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚才修理完毕回来而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说，总之…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.72,0:05:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我变成幽灵了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.62,0:05:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请容我不予置评
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.29,0:05:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么这样…那我再也不能\N跟大家说话了是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.56,0:05:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.83,0:05:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能一起吃蛋糕，一起玩耍\N也不能一起工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.03,0:05:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事都不能做了是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.23,0:05:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个时候真的笑翻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有那么好笑吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得薄荷秃头的时候\N比较好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.14,0:05:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎哟，干嘛把八百年前的事\N拿出来讲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.41,0:05:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光溜溜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.88,0:05:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明明已经死了\N大家却好像还是很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓人情淡薄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.49,0:05:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，香草一定在心里想着你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.46,0:05:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.19,0:06:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是为了保护大家才死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.83,0:06:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然那么快就把我忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.73,0:06:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要雪恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.90,0:06:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，不要变成怨灵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.31,0:06:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是有办法可以活过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.77,0:06:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.14,0:06:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前些时候回收的遗失文明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.15,0:06:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说可以用来交换灵魂喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交换灵魂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.09,0:06:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，虽然身体是用别人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.16,0:06:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，总比死掉来得好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有，那个时候的薄荷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.79,0:06:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托，请不要再讲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想用谁的身体都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.40,0:06:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯有香草请放过她喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.94,0:06:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我用了别人的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.47,0:06:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么那个人\N就会代替我死掉对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.04,0:06:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们本来就该死了\N只不过是你用自己的生命救了他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.21,0:06:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你死了\N这些人也是笑得跟白痴一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用为他们想那么多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.79,0:07:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，他们一直都是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.06,0:07:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使队成军两周年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家好好庆祝一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.83,0:07:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，你在干什么\N别碍事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.77,0:07:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，讨厌\N好像踩到什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.90,0:07:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优\N你要把地板擦干净喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.71,0:07:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家快一点\N不然乐透要卖光了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.81,0:07:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.35,0:07:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.38,0:07:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家原本也很想去买乐透\N来享受那种兴奋感的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是说这个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.19,0:07:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.09,0:07:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好…好恐怖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.16,0:07:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使队成军两周年又三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.40,0:07:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟大家一起庆祝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.03,0:07:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的很想庆祝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.00,0:07:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，听说基地涌出温泉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得快点去泡才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.50,0:07:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温泉蛋是我的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.54,0:07:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也想去泡温泉对不对？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.64,0:07:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，温泉我是泡到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.05,0:08:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，只剩下温泉蛋的蛋壳而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.95,0:08:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要雪恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.05,0:08:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，这一切都变成了\N大家美好的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.83,0:08:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论是好事还是坏事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.00,0:08:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了今天\N都变成大家开心的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.17,0:08:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.34,0:08:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想烤个蛋糕给大家吃\N可是烤焦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.85,0:08:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比"布吉屋"的蛋糕好吃多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.82,0:08:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.39,0:08:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，我说你啊\N打起精神来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哭丧的脸不适合你唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.23,0:08:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，那我就不管你愿不愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.27,0:08:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要做罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.71,0:09:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，你为什么喜欢大海呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.74,0:09:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为很像我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.75,0:09:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实大家都是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.78,0:09:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是没错啦，虽然其中\N也有一些微妙的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.86,0:09:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.30,0:09:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样…这样就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样真的好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.08,0:09:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照这样下去\N你可能没办法存在太久喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.61,0:09:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我会死是我自己造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.65,0:09:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，你这个人真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，聊得好开心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.89,0:09:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全沉醉在回忆的话题中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.26,0:09:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉好清爽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.13,0:09:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.93,0:09:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，兰花，薄荷，香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,华克中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.40,0:10:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好想再跟大家聊聊天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.22,0:10:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使队成军纪念蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.86,0:10:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论是二十周年\N还是五十周年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.53,0:10:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都想做给你们吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.33,0:10:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.74,0:10:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，看来已经没有机会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.74,0:10:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经快要看不见你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.08,0:10:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见了，各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.38,0:10:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的很喜欢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很喜欢天使队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.82,0:10:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等一下，不太对劲喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.09,0:10:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逐渐消失的不是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是佛特他们耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.46,0:11:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！我的身体…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.86,0:11:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底出了什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.87,0:11:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我总觉得\N我们好像忘记了什么事耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.80,0:11:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，我记得我们不是正在战斗吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.18,0:11:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，然后梅尔优拿着\N敌军投来的手榴弹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.39,0:11:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，对了，我想起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.43,0:11:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之，被炸死的是佛特他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.70,0:11:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了成佛而述说着\N他们对这个世间的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.21,0:11:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅琳少校，我送人事命令来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.28,0:11:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人事命令？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什么人事命令？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.58,0:11:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.55,0:12:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.19,0:12:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#02  异动乌龙面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？更换队长？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.56,0:12:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从今天起，梅琳少校\N将成为你们天使队的指挥官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.00,0:12:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我则接掌双子星队的指挥官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.34,0:12:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情来得真突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.37,0:12:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根据高层长官的说法是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.14,0:12:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,双子星队成立以来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.74,0:12:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和天使队之间的差距\N越来越大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.41,0:12:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每位队员的能力应该都差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.12,0:12:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以这可能是\N指挥官的能力差异所造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.42,0:12:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.65,0:12:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亏你还笑得出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.69,0:12:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是在说你无能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.09,0:12:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.83,0:12:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们在一起那么久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.16,0:12:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的好舍不得喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.86,0:12:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(吵闹)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你从刚才心情好像就很不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.00,0:12:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别看我这样\N我可是同期生中最有成就的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.14,0:12:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明如此，却叫我来带\N你们这群蠢材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.38,0:13:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说谁是蠢材？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.11,0:13:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家冷静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.45,0:13:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后你们要一起\N相处下去不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.89,0:13:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.89,0:13:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然大家都是蠢材\N那就好好相处吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说谁是蠢材？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.56,0:13:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-你欠揍啊，蠢蛋\N-快放开我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.16,0:13:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暴风雨的预感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.90,0:13:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紧急警报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.97,0:13:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首都上空出现UFO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.87,0:13:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,双子星队、天使队\N请立刻紧急出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.51,0:13:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，开工了开工了，大家出动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.74,0:13:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点把事情解决掉\N然后去吃饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.71,0:13:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛\N你们居然转变得这么快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.42,0:13:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不干喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.72,0:13:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不要跟这些家伙一起工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，这是军方的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.99,0:13:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我不要也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.53,0:13:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.33,0:13:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油加油，梅琳加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.70,0:13:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油加油，梅琳加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你们，我的啦啦队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.87,0:13:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会认输，我会好好加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.67,0:13:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个还在玩什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.64,0:14:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请快点出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.44,0:14:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使队已经出击了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.81,0:14:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就交给他们去打啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.61,0:14:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易从啰嗦的\N梅琳少校的魔掌解脱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.92,0:14:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是纪念日，要放假一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可以这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.25,0:14:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们不好好表现的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.56,0:14:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还是会被减薪的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,满口都是钱，你很烦耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.86,0:14:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的钱到底花到哪里去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.76,0:14:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正一定是打小钢珠\N玩赛马，还有买少女漫画吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可可莫，可可莫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是胡子啦，胡子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.07,0:14:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校的胡子\N每天都上美容院修整唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？那么讲究啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.61,0:14:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光是胡子用的保养液\N一个月就要好几十万
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贵的要命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.18,0:14:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,，原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那胡子\N明明一点都不适合他的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是因为很逊所以才更爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.89,0:14:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像越笨的孩子越有人爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.79,0:14:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪异的嗜好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.13,0:14:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，如果要花那么多钱的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.79,0:14:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还不如戒掉这种奇怪的讲究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把胡子刮掉不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说对不对？中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们不要太瞧不起人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.77,0:15:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们这两个死小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.74,0:15:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们现在踩到我的地雷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.54,0:15:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们做好觉悟了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.98,0:15:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？他生气了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.01,0:15:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然敢瞧不起我的胡子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.78,0:15:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们准备接受惩罚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.62,0:15:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别跑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.39,0:15:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么回事？\N我们才刚击退UFO回来而已耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.03,0:15:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在正要去吃饭耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.99,0:15:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先别说了，你们看看那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.00,0:15:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是华克中校吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那两个人交出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.64,0:15:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.57,0:15:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托请救救我们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不晓得出了什么事\N可是他们已经说不要了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.91,0:15:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊，不晓得出了什么事\N不过，这一定是中校的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.01,0:15:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就乖乖的回去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.05,0:15:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(吵闹)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.35,0:15:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然敢打我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.49,0:15:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是华克中校\N我也饶不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.09,0:15:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要好好教训你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.06,0:15:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有意思！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.96,0:16:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然，我是不晓得出了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.46,0:16:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，中校变回大战时的个性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是"白超新星之狼"？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花很危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.67,0:16:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会有这种事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我居然会被这个老头…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.31,0:16:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.38,0:16:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我…输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.05,0:16:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花变成石像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.49,0:16:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"战败之石"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.62,0:16:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战败之石？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.59,0:16:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我曾经在书上看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在心里认输的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.92,0:16:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会变成一个\N被称为"战败之石"的石像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.89,0:16:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，学校里的石像\N也是那么来的对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.50,0:16:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们学校也有战败之石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.67,0:16:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要也把你们变成石像？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.07,0:16:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.18,0:16:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好喝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.85,0:16:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么另类的敌人\N根本是我管辖之外的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.65,0:16:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么好拼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.25,0:17:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事交给天使队应付就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.25,0:17:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(之后，梅琳将大难临头)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.72,0:17:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(冲击的瞬间在3分16秒后)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.66,0:17:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷？你是在叫我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.73,0:17:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是薄荷的好友\N她拜托我来帮忙大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫玛朵玛洁儿  ．  酷酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭候大驾多时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.68,0:17:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来由我的\N机器人好友们来对付你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.05,0:17:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.15,0:17:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有效了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.89,0:17:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干的好！薄荷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.42,0:17:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，薄荷的好友\N玛朵玛洁儿．酷酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.06,0:17:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他居然在笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.60,0:17:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经尽力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.27,0:17:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷的好友\N也变成战败之石了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.07,0:17:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有其它办法了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.31,0:17:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光是逃根本没有用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.11,0:18:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捡起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.51,0:18:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说来，我还没有跟你比过\N谁的枪法比较快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.15,0:18:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样太危险了啦，佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.12,0:18:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们趁现在快点到城里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.12,0:18:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.99,0:18:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们在干嘛，快走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听好了，喊三二一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喊完三二一就拔枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.50,0:18:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始罗，三…二…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.83,0:18:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.67,0:18:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会这样，为什么不拔枪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.08,0:18:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校，你果然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.51,0:18:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他又追来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.18,0:18:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的愤怒居然能持续那么久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.09,0:18:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校到底在气什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.52,0:18:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？胡子吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.52,0:18:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊\N他好像很喜欢他的胡子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.49,0:18:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.53,0:18:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跑累了，跑不动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你们先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.10,0:18:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你嘴巴虽然这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实你是想留下来拖延时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好让大家逃走对不对？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.60,0:19:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦\N香草，大家一起逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经跑不动了，所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我也陪你留下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.02,0:19:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.02,0:19:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可可莫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.32,0:19:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们两个先去找救援吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.92,0:19:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,华克中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.62,0:19:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有话跟你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.86,0:19:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的胡子好帅气喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.40,0:19:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我从以前就一直觉得\N你的胡子好帅气喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可可莫跟马利普
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.10,0:19:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是因为自己没有\N那么帅气的胡子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.11,0:19:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心生嫉妒所以才会那么说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.91,0:19:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不对啊？香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.61,0:19:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该说是有跟没有都一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.95,0:19:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实大家根本\N没有在看你的胡子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.55,0:19:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你自己太自恋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.78,0:19:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不愧是香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不会以谎言来说服别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.65,0:19:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.12,0:19:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准瞧不起我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.59,0:19:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果…果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.13,0:19:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.86,0:19:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.17,0:20:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且感觉火气比刚才还要大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.07,0:20:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得快去找救援才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.57,0:20:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，有人在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.64,0:20:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀\N没想到这两个人真的在交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(距离梅琳大难临头瞬间还有…)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.18,0:20:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.85,0:20:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可可莫，马利普
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.39,0:20:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.75,0:20:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还以为是谁呢\N原来是梅琳少校啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.56,0:20:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请救救我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.76,0:20:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在有点事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.10,0:20:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不晓得帮不帮得上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.13,0:20:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了，要来了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅琳少校，你要去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.74,0:20:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有啦，我要拿武器啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.17,0:20:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为这里有蛮好用的棒子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.61,0:20:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,棒子？你以为用棒子\N就能打倒那家伙吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.75,0:20:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于被我追到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.45,0:20:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快啊，少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用那根棒子也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.25,0:20:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下\N我还没做好心理准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.55,0:20:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.56,0:20:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.79,0:20:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"WON球棒"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.06,0:20:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.13,0:21:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,扥朗斯巴传说中的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.86,0:21:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,据说拿着这个武器的人\N一定会获得胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.67,0:21:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是胜利"WIN"的过去式\N"WON"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.80,0:21:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,WON球棒，这东西真好用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.47,0:21:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手持"WON球棒"的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会化成巨大的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.61,0:21:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消灭所有邪恶的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.61,0:21:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是古老的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨大的身体？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.75,0:21:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎么会变成这样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.18,0:21:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油啊，勇者！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.75,0:21:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请消灭邪恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.72,0:21:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请连我们的份一起加油，勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.29,0:21:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被你们擅自期待\N我也会很困扰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.30,0:21:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油啊，勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.00,0:21:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.27,0:21:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油加油，梅琳加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油加油，梅琳加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了啦，我打就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们别看我这样\N在军官学校的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.31,0:21:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是人称"金色怒吼流星"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.51,0:21:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就让你看看我的威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.75,0:21:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看招！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.19,0:21:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看个头啦
